title: #92Noon - Our Community in Crisis
description: Thanks to Courtney Cronin, Chad Greenway & Korzo for joining the show today, to add perspective to the ongoing riots in the Mpls/St Paul area. PA & Charch discuss aspects of it, and we air the Governor's press conference at 10:30.
